item.description:
Saturday May 10th is the Boston Demons annual Trivia Night.

This is always a very popular event on our calendar so get your teams organized now for a top night of trivia, prizes, finger foods, and perhaps a pick from the infamous "Showcase of Shite." Grab as many mates as you can and get along to Tommy Doyles Kendall Sq, 7pm for a 7:30 start. Support your local footy club and see you on the 10th.

The Demons always put on a good night, this should be fun!

Cheers,
Damien
